Package lt.viko.eif.vskuder.model

Class Game

java.lang.Object
lt.viko.eif.vskuder.model.Game
@Entity public class Game extends Object
The Game class represents a game object with its properties such as id, title, price, developer, and categories. This class is mapped to a database table named "Game" using JPA annotations. It also has JAXB annotations for XML binding.
